The Planning Commission takes action on various planning issues. The Commission meets on the first and third Wednesday’s of the month (unless otherwise noted) at 6:00 pm in the City Council Chambers located at 2600 Fresno Street, 2nd floor. Meetings are open to the public and also air on televisoin. For air times, please visit http://cmac.tv. For additional information, please call (559) 621-8277.
